{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 3 shows a qualitative example of this.",
    "In terms of the differences between models, we observe that CTRLSum summaries are more extractive than BRIO summaries, containing more document entities (predicted or gold) in the output.",
    "We also found that BRIO summaries suffer a lot from entity hallucination, which can be alleviated by CTRLSum methods.",
    "GPT-4 summaries are considered the closest to the gold summaries for the following reasons: First, they contain as many gold entities as the CTRLSum summaries but with more subjective coherence.",
    "Second, they have the least hallucinated entities compared to the other two models."
  ]
}